Package: tisch
Title: A Formula-Based Table Generator for LaTeX Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Christian", "Rubba", email = "cran@christianrubba.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: tisch provides a formula-based interface for generating tabular
    outputs for LaTeX documents. The formula interface is based on reshape2's
    casting function and allows users to assign variables to columns and rows.
    tisch assand the arrangement of cell values. A theming
    system gives easy control over aesthetic aspects of the tables.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    reshape2,
    infuser
Suggests: 
    broom
License: MIT
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.0
